Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又变得不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟在这边 还是在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白自己身处于那边的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我们连接在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我… 真正的我到底在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 真正的我根本就不存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只存在于他人的记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在说着这番话的我 …是我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 究竟是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不需要肉体吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为爱丽丝做的事 全都是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}重置一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不是还没吃完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说在减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事没必要说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天可能会有货物送来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是货到付款
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的话就付一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是计算机的配件？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 今晚你会和我们一起去玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去Cyberia Cyberia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我发下邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要给谁发邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道又是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你说谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 四方田千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前出于爱丽丝的一番好意 才带她去了一次Cyberia
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她倒好 跟我们像陌路人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请她也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 只是心中泛起了一种奇怪的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的思绪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆中没有的事 就是没发生过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆中没有的人 从一开始就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 没在说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…布！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪 又是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这台不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那台也改装得很别致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦 快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在等我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该猜拳了吧 猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎 我们不等你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狡猾 快点猜拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种破公司 我再也不想干了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让我做那种事… 老子不干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子不干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子不干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 死也不干了 这次绝对要辞职…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆中没有的事 就是没发生过的事 记忆只是一份记录
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}把记录改写掉就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Present Day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Present Time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为把自己从所有人的记忆中消除了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是你所期望的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人因此离奇地死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人因此受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的信息再也不会从连线世界中流出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以玲音 你不用继续存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你所期望的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的这番话 就像那个人说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人一开始就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算存在 他也不会妄图想成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是如此 那么我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不是说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连线世界不是现实世界的上级目录
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的想法是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络是传送信息的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息不会停留在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息始终是流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的记忆 个人发生的事 人类历史上发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 还有共享中的无意识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能存储如此庞大的记忆的东西 光凭人类能做得出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来连线世界只是用来连接的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 连接的另一端通往哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类有必要了解这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:14:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对此一无所知 人类不是依旧走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类创造了他们各自信奉的神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且深信世界就如他们所想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算讨厌 那也是玲音 也就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 玲音你不是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音是普遍存在的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音是观察者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 玲音就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做神多轻松呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比做人轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在那儿看着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会鄙视玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会讨厌玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从头来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易重置了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 那么你又是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(972,998)\fs40}背负
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 不用再穿那种东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40\fad(100,100)}（这句话有双重含义，请结合之前的画面去理解。）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 下次我给你泡好喝的红茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 到时候一定要再配上玛德琳蛋糕 味道可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆并不只是过去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还连接着现在和未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才心胸宽广的我欣然接受了你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以卧室的窗帘要交给我来选
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切听从你的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 孺子可教也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前见过吗？好像见过吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是我实习任教的那所学校里的学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好像也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是第一次见面呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很洋化的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我自己也觉得难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 无论何时我们都能相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们永远都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
